		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_64499763">I'll sound pessimistic / sceptic here, but this seems just a normal Android tablet with a LCD 60Hz screen and a special color profile configuration to mimic an e-Ink screen. But it's not an e-ink display as Malik mentions, that's for sure.

I could (and be delighted to) be wrong, but this seems to me an overpriced, overhyped tablet. We'll see if we don't have here another Theranos/Juicero scenario.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_64499763">
